net.vivialconnect.model.connector

Class PhoneNumber

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.vivialconnect.model.VivialConnectResource
      • net.vivialconnect.model.connector.PhoneNumber
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class PhoneNumber
extends VivialConnectResource
    In the API, the phone_numbers resource allows you to associate or disassociate phone numbers from a Connector. When creating or editing a phone number association, you must provide a phone_number or phone_number_id for a phone number you own. Currently, a phone number can only be associated with a single Connector.

    This class represents a phone number entity that can operated over a connector.
